# Various helper scripts of daily life

*mkv2mp4.sh*

Convert mkv video files to mp4 so that it can be played natively by ipad or macos.
video/audio streams are copied so no transcoding involved.
It has to be sure that video/audio encoding is supported format (e.g. x264).

*extractaudio.sh*

Copy audio stream from video files.
No transcoding is done.

*tmclean.sh*

Clean local cached snapshot of TimeMachine to free some space.

